channel.title: Making a no-ip server?
channel.description:
1. Ok so I downloaded a tutorial. I went through the steps until it says: To download JDK 6.0... I went to the site to download it. I then had to click out of it. I try to install it again but it says its already installed.
2.Now... I go to find my router... It is not on the list.
3.ALSO.. When I open my server.. and I log in on any account, it says:
"Infinity: character file could not be found Infinity: error writing file Infinity: error writing file Infinity: error writing file Infinity: error writing file Infinity: error writing file Etc...
Anyone wanna help? [br][size=1]Posted on: May 24, 2007, 05:51:57 PM[/size][hr]On number 1.. Im re-installing JDK 6.0 Update 1 right now.... and BTW
[size=11pt]I'm looking for a person to team with me on a server (Coder). Im pretty new at the FTL[/size]
